descriptionNullable: The VGChartz Network is a collection of five video game websites: VGChartz, gamrFeed, gamrReview, gamrTV, and gamrConnect. VGChartz sits at the center of the network and is a video game sales tracking website, providing weekly sales figures of console software and hardware by region. The site was launched in June 2005 and is owned by Brett Walton. VGChartz provides tools for worldwide data analysis and regular reviews of the data it provides.
